## Key Design Decisions

| Decision | Rationale |
|---|---|
| `value` prop on `StepperItem` and `StepperPanel` | Matches `TabsTrigger`/`TabsContent` API convention in shadcn |
| `StepperSeparator` is a sibling of `StepperItem` | More flexible layout; separator reads orientation from root `StepperContext` via `group/stepper` selectors |
| Two contexts (`StepperContext` + `StepperItemContext`) | Root context carries global state; item context carries per-step state for `StepperTrigger` to read |
| `data-active={isActive \|\| undefined}` pattern | Omits attribute when false (matches Tabs, Sidebar patterns); avoids `data-active="false"` anti-pattern |
| `StepperPanel` renders `null` when inactive | Avoids hidden DOM subtree; matches `TabsContent` behavior in base-ui version |
| `"use client"` on both component and example | Required due to `useState`, `useCallback`, `useMemo` usage |

